name: Abandoned skull
description: The word alone sends shudders down a sensitive spine, troubling the thoughts of pained souls as their hurt swells in ripples. It is a sentence of undesired solitude often pronounced on the innocent, the trusting—administered without warning or satisfactory cause.Some poisons have no antidote, but are slow, silent, torturous ends that curl up the broken body swept into a cold, dark corner. The feeling of abandonment overwhelmed me as I realised that no one had waited, or cared where I was
